Loral to sell $ 600 mln of convertible prfd . Loral Space & Communications Ltd said Friday that it has agreed to sell $ 600 million of six percent convertible preferred equivalent obligations due 2006 . The figure includes the exercise of over - allotment option . The securities will be convertible into common shares at $ 20 per share , a premium of 25 . 9 percent over Thursday ' s closing at 15 - 7 / 8 , the company said . 
